p: The industry fatty acid esters (FAME) mix 37 standard for fatty acids analysis was purchased from Bellefonte, PA (USA). The purity of CO 2 used for SC-CO 2 extraction was 99.97% ( w/ w) (Messer, Osijek, Croatia). All other chemicals and reagents were of analytical reagent grade and obtained from Sigma–Aldrich (St. Louis, MO, USA) and 3-( N-morpholino)propanesulfonic acid was purchased from Sigma–Aldrich (Chemie GmbH, Taufkirchen, Germany).
